m wp-image-74 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost:8080/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/hotel2-300x166.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"166\" /></blockquote>', 'Más sobre el castillo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '73-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-08-10 00:41:47', '2018-08-10 00:41:47', '', 73, 'http://localhost:8080/2018/08/10/73-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
